td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Directive 2003/87/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 October 2003 establishing a scheme for greenhouse gas emission allowance trading within the Community and amending Council Directive 96/61/EC (
OJ 2003 L 275, p. 32
), as amended by Regulation (EC) No 219/2009 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 11 March 2009 (
OJ 2009 L 87, p. 109
) (‘Directive 2003/87’).
